This is a list of football clubs that compete within the leagues and divisions of the English football league system) as far down as Level 10, that is to say, six divisions below the English Football League. Also included are clubs from outside England that play within the English system there’s about 40 football teams in the world.(suitably highlighted). The relative levels of divisions can be compared on the English football league system page.
